1
00:01:28,000 --> 00:01:33,000
"Bittersweet Love."

2
00:01:34,724 --> 00:01:35,724
Xiaofan.

3
00:01:36,140 --> 00:01:37,980
I'll be staying at
Lüqing's place for a while.

4
00:01:38,932 --> 00:01:39,932
So...

5
00:01:40,265 --> 00:01:42,224
I'm afraid I'll have to
ask you to move out.

6
00:01:51,640 --> 00:01:52,349
Let's get acquainted.

7
00:01:52,432 --> 00:01:53,432
My name is Li Wenxi.

8
00:01:53,474 --> 00:01:54,599
Who is Li Wenxi?

9
00:01:54,974 --> 00:01:55,849
Li Wenxi.

10
00:01:55,890 --> 00:01:57,807
They're childhood bosom buddies.

11
00:01:58,057 --> 00:01:59,057
Do you know what's

12
00:01:59,058 --> 00:02:00,682
the most valuable thing about you?

13
00:02:00,890 --> 00:02:02,432
It's that you know your place.

14
00:02:04,724 --> 00:02:05,724
Oh.

15
00:02:30,432 --> 00:02:31,432
Bro.

16
00:02:31,849 --> 00:02:32,849
The soup on the stove

17
00:02:33,224 --> 00:02:34,944
just needs to simmer for another half hour.

18
00:03:06,974 --> 00:03:07,974
I...

19
00:03:13,307 --> 00:03:14,307
I'll be going then.

20
00:03:58,807 --> 00:04:00,849
Midnight, camped by the door?

21
00:04:01,307 --> 00:04:01,890
Aunt Lin.
Not at school?

22
00:04:03,849 --> 00:04:04,849
Aunt Lin.

23
00:04:05,599 --> 00:04:07,349
The dorm closed early.

24
00:04:07,890 --> 00:04:09,090
I didn't make it back in time.

25
00:04:09,349 --> 00:04:11,432
Out wandering this late?

26
00:04:14,474 --> 00:04:15,474
Xiaofan.

27
00:04:16,432 --> 00:04:17,599
Listen, dear.

28
00:04:18,807 --> 00:04:20,724
After all,

29
00:04:20,765 --> 00:04:22,265
you‘re at the same school as Lüqing.

30
00:04:24,057 --> 00:04:26,099
Even if he's graduated,

31
00:04:26,515 --> 00:04:27,639
he still has many fellow disciples

32
00:04:27,640 --> 00:04:28,849
on campus.

33
00:04:29,349 --> 00:04:30,681
You need to behave yourself at school.

34
00:04:30,682 --> 00:04:32,265
Don't bring shame on Lüqing.

35
00:04:33,515 --> 00:04:34,515
I understand.

36
00:04:37,682 --> 00:04:38,682
I understand.

37
00:04:42,265 --> 00:04:43,265
Yeah.

38
00:04:45,640 --> 00:04:46,640
I brought shame on him.

39
00:06:01,300 --> 00:06:03,300
(Episode 5)

40
00:06:04,849 --> 00:06:05,849
Xiaofan.

41
00:06:06,140 --> 00:06:07,140
Come. Sit.

42
00:06:12,182 --> 00:06:13,182
Xiaofan.

43
00:06:13,474 --> 00:06:14,954
You're about to graduate, aren't you?

44
00:06:15,557 --> 00:06:16,557
Yes, Uncle Bei.

45
00:06:18,307 --> 00:06:20,107
Would you like to go
for a bachelor's degree?

46
00:06:25,057 --> 00:06:26,417
No, I don't want to keep studying.

47
00:06:29,307 --> 00:06:30,557
Then so be it.

48
00:06:31,515 --> 00:06:33,682
Starting work early isn't such a bad idea.

49
00:06:33,974 --> 00:06:34,974
I'll be going now.

50
00:06:35,432 --> 00:06:36,432
Wait a moment.

51
00:06:37,057 --> 00:06:38,265
As for Xiaofan's job...

52
00:06:42,849 --> 00:06:43,849
I think

53
00:06:43,974 --> 00:06:45,849
we should still respect his wishes.

54
00:06:46,807 --> 00:06:49,467
He has a mind of his own.

55
00:06:51,932 --> 00:06:52,932
Bye.

56
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:14,000
Xiaofan,

57
00:07:14,083 --> 00:07:16,041
here's the number for your new workplace.

58
00:07:16,333 --> 00:07:18,666
Since you chose to start working early,
give it your all.

59
00:07:19,083 --> 00:07:22,416
The Bei's family won't let you down.

60
00:07:29,386 --> 00:07:31,533
[Sales Branch]

61
00:07:34,682 --> 00:07:35,682
Hello.

62
00:07:35,849 --> 00:07:36,849
I'm Lu Xiaofan.

63
00:07:37,057 --> 00:07:38,257
Here to report for duty today.

64
00:07:39,140 --> 00:07:39,890
Xiaofan, you've arrived!

65
00:07:40,140 --> 00:07:41,460
Come, come, have a seat. Come on.

66
00:07:41,599 --> 00:07:42,599
Come here.

67
00:07:42,849 --> 00:07:43,889
I've been waiting for you.

68
00:07:44,265 --> 00:07:45,265
Come on, sit, sit.

69
00:07:45,349 --> 00:07:46,349
Oh.

70
00:07:46,474 --> 00:07:47,474
Xiaofan.

71
00:07:47,515 --> 00:07:48,557
Work hard, all right?

72
00:07:48,765 --> 00:07:49,805
I have high hopes for you.

73
00:08:28,916 --> 00:08:31,583
Bro, you haven't been home in ages.

74
00:08:32,166 --> 00:08:33,916
You never come visit me.

75
00:08:34,250 --> 00:08:37,375
That annoying Lu Xiaofan watches films
in the living room all day.

76
00:08:37,791 --> 00:08:39,875
He blubbers late at night
and drives me nuts.

77
00:08:39,875 --> 00:08:41,708
Get yourself a hobby or something.

78
00:08:42,166 --> 00:08:43,666
I go home every couple of weeks.

79
00:08:44,625 --> 00:08:46,500
I'm swamped, bye for now.

80
00:09:05,700 --> 00:09:08,100
(Two Years Later)

81
00:09:23,979 --> 00:09:25,339
[Xiaoping is calling]

82
00:09:28,057 --> 00:09:28,724
Xiaofan.
What's the emergency?

83
00:09:29,765 --> 00:09:31,224
Couldn't this wait until after work?

84
00:09:31,349 --> 00:09:31,849
Brother.

85
00:09:32,182 --> 00:09:33,515
Didn't you page me?

86
00:09:34,890 --> 00:09:36,765
Mom booked a train for next week.

87
00:09:36,890 --> 00:09:37,890
Remember to pick her up.

88
00:09:38,224 --> 00:09:39,265
Mom's coming to Yunjing?

89
00:09:40,307 --> 00:09:41,599
Ask Old Wu to pick her up.

90
00:09:41,765 --> 00:09:43,182
He's a careful driver.

91
00:09:44,099 --> 00:09:46,140
Been ages, no thought of coming home.

92
00:09:46,682 --> 00:09:47,682
Oh, right...

93
00:09:47,765 --> 00:09:48,765
Mom specifically said
she wants to see Lüxin.

94
00:09:52,515 --> 00:09:53,806
Mom wants to see Lüxin?

95
00:09:53,807 --> 00:09:54,807
Why?

96
00:09:54,932 --> 00:09:56,772
Can't a mother-in-law
see her daughter-in-law?

97
00:09:58,182 --> 00:09:59,640
Return tickets are hard to come by.

98
00:09:59,682 --> 00:10:00,599
Book them early.

99
00:10:00,640 --> 00:10:01,849
She's flying too?

100
00:10:01,974 --> 00:10:03,640
It's such a long trip for Mom to Yunjing.

101
00:10:03,724 --> 00:10:05,140
She deserves to enjoy herself.

102
00:10:06,540 --> 00:10:07,165
All right.

103
00:10:07,474 --> 00:10:08,634
I'll cover the plane tickets.

104
00:10:09,015 --> 00:10:10,895
We still need a letter from the workplace unit.

105
00:10:11,724 --> 00:10:13,432
Just have Old Wu book the tickets.

106
00:10:13,890 --> 00:10:16,140
The Beis need an
introduction letter for tickets?

107
00:10:16,224 --> 00:10:17,224
Oh, right.

108
00:10:17,349 --> 00:10:17,932
Mom also said

109
00:10:18,182 --> 00:10:19,682
she's bringing the little one.

110
00:10:19,807 --> 00:10:20,847
Let her broaden her views.

111
00:10:22,182 --> 00:10:23,599
Okay, got it.

112
00:10:23,640 --> 00:10:24,182
All right then.

113
00:10:24,390 --> 00:10:25,390
I'll hang up now.

114
00:10:25,474 --> 00:10:26,754
You know what's expected of you.

115
00:10:40,724 --> 00:10:41,724
Aunt Lin.

116
00:10:42,140 --> 00:10:43,223
Is Uncle Bei not home?

117
00:10:43,224 --> 00:10:44,224
Mr. Bei?

118
00:10:44,265 --> 00:10:45,450
He's gone to a conference out of town.

119
00:10:45,474 --> 00:10:46,682
He'll be away for two weeks.

120
00:10:57,765 --> 00:10:59,390
What's your family up to now?

121
00:11:01,557 --> 00:11:03,265
My parents are coming to Yunjing.

122
00:11:04,307 --> 00:11:05,765
Then just entertain them as usual.

123
00:11:05,849 --> 00:11:07,649
Don't bother Mr. Bei
with every little thing.

124
00:11:10,390 --> 00:11:11,390
Lüxin.

125
00:11:11,682 --> 00:11:12,182
Lüxin.
What is it?

126
00:11:15,349 --> 00:11:16,349
Nothing.

127
00:11:16,640 --> 00:11:17,640
It's nothing.

128
00:11:19,349 --> 00:11:20,724
Take this in for me.

129
00:12:03,349 --> 00:12:04,349
You're here!

130
00:12:05,307 --> 00:12:06,307
Boss.

131
00:12:06,474 --> 00:12:07,640
Any new releases lately?

132
00:12:07,849 --> 00:12:08,515
Sure.

133
00:12:08,516 --> 00:12:09,916
Lots. Which one do you want to see?

134
00:12:12,807 --> 00:12:13,557
What's that one?

135
00:12:13,807 --> 00:12:14,807
A wuxia film.

136
00:12:15,099 --> 00:12:16,349
Brigitte Lin in male disguise.

137
00:12:16,974 --> 00:12:17,974
I'll take that one.

138
00:12:19,432 --> 00:12:20,432
I like Brigitte Lin too.

139
00:12:21,515 --> 00:12:22,640
No one but Brigitte Lin

140
00:12:23,099 --> 00:12:24,515
could play Lian Nichang so well.

141
00:12:25,099 --> 00:12:26,741
Sadly, Lian Nichang had
a humble background.

142
00:12:26,765 --> 00:12:29,640
Had she not loved
noble-born Zhuo Yihang,

143
00:12:29,765 --> 00:12:31,682
she wouldn't be like this.

144
00:12:32,557 --> 00:12:33,557
What a shame.

145
00:12:39,890 --> 00:12:40,557
I'm off, boss.

146
00:12:40,807 --> 00:12:41,807
Sure.

147
00:12:42,057 --> 00:12:43,057
Take care. Come again.

148
00:12:54,140 --> 00:12:54,807
Aunt Lin.
Oh!

149
00:12:55,849 --> 00:12:56,849
Xiaofan.

150
00:12:57,224 --> 00:12:59,182
Back so late. No dinner left for you.

151
00:12:59,849 --> 00:13:00,849
It's fine, Aunt Lin.

152
00:13:01,265 --> 00:13:02,474
You go get some rest.

153
00:13:03,474 --> 00:13:04,754
Well, I'll leave you alone then.

154
00:14:01,015 --> 00:14:03,140
It's so handy having a phone at your unit.

155
00:14:03,390 --> 00:14:05,014
Has the dinner with Lüxin for Mom

156
00:14:05,015 --> 00:14:05,932
been arranged?
Working on it.

157
00:14:06,974 --> 00:14:09,224
Why must it be so
troublesome for them to meet?

158
00:14:09,474 --> 00:14:10,474
Honestly.

159
00:14:10,890 --> 00:14:11,890
Don't worry.

160
00:14:12,265 --> 00:14:12,974
I'm at work.
I'll get it arranged.

161
00:14:13,890 --> 00:14:14,890
What are you playing at?
With that job of yours,

162
00:14:16,015 --> 00:14:17,415
what urgent matters could you have?

163
00:14:47,182 --> 00:14:48,182
Who's there?

164
00:14:50,224 --> 00:14:51,224
It's me.

165
00:14:54,307 --> 00:14:55,307
Bro.

166
00:14:55,515 --> 00:14:56,515
Long time no see.

167
00:14:57,682 --> 00:14:59,307
So what brings you here?

168
00:15:01,224 --> 00:15:02,765
Is your family asking for money again?

169
00:15:03,765 --> 00:15:06,015
Or is your brother
unhappy with his job again?

170
00:15:07,182 --> 00:15:08,349
Or something else?

171
00:15:09,724 --> 00:15:11,057
My mother said

172
00:15:11,265 --> 00:15:13,224
she wants to visit me in Yunjing.

173
00:15:13,599 --> 00:15:15,557
They're arriving. Could you host them?

174
00:15:17,015 --> 00:15:19,890
She also wants to see Lüxin.

175
00:15:23,140 --> 00:15:24,140
How about

176
00:15:25,015 --> 00:15:26,432
giving her a call?

177
00:15:27,265 --> 00:15:27,765
All right.

178
00:15:28,099 --> 00:15:29,099
I got it.

179
00:15:31,807 --> 00:15:32,807
Bro.

180
00:15:33,474 --> 00:15:34,890
You really won't eat?

181
00:15:36,224 --> 00:15:37,224
Not hungry.

182
00:15:39,307 --> 00:15:40,307
Well,

183
00:15:42,390 --> 00:15:43,390
I'm leaving.

184
00:16:07,640 --> 00:16:10,200
(Two years earlier) I'll be staying
at Lüqing's place for a while.

185
00:16:10,224 --> 00:16:12,390
I'm afraid I'll have to
ask you to move out.

186
00:16:20,140 --> 00:16:21,140
Bro.

187
00:16:22,010 --> 00:16:23,677
I'll be going then.

188
00:16:39,640 --> 00:16:40,640
You see?

189
00:16:40,765 --> 00:16:43,057
He couldn't even look me in the face.

190
00:16:44,224 --> 00:16:46,432
What courage or standing

191
00:16:47,182 --> 00:16:48,542
could he have to face your mother?

192
00:16:52,682 --> 00:16:54,474
You know better than anyone

193
00:16:55,182 --> 00:16:56,765
what your mother did to me back then.

194
00:16:59,265 --> 00:17:01,015
Wonder how he'll react, right?

195
00:17:02,307 --> 00:17:03,390
Will he cry?

196
00:17:04,765 --> 00:17:07,057
Will he... fight for it?

197
00:17:08,974 --> 00:17:11,265
But you're too proud to ask him.

198
00:17:12,640 --> 00:17:13,640
Is he just...

199
00:17:14,265 --> 00:17:17,140
simply seeking your help?

200
00:17:24,599 --> 00:17:25,599
Maybe it's for the best.

201
00:17:26,890 --> 00:17:28,349
Better split early

202
00:17:28,765 --> 00:17:29,849
than have your mom find out

203
00:17:30,265 --> 00:17:31,474
and step in.

204
00:17:48,932 --> 00:17:50,182
I'm honestly curious.

205
00:17:51,307 --> 00:17:53,099
How could you fall for a man like him?

206
00:17:57,932 --> 00:17:59,932
Mind your own business.

207
00:18:01,765 --> 00:18:03,640
The only connection between us now

208
00:18:04,599 --> 00:18:06,474
is that money left in Gangcheng.

209
00:18:10,724 --> 00:18:12,057
Whatever you plan to do,

210
00:18:13,015 --> 00:18:14,057
I can help you.

211
00:18:17,349 --> 00:18:19,140
More like I'm the one helping you.

212
00:18:22,057 --> 00:18:24,099
Info from the old man,

213
00:18:24,515 --> 00:18:26,140
sent straight to Li Wenxi.

214
00:18:27,557 --> 00:18:29,015
Letting him operate overseas.

215
00:18:32,224 --> 00:18:33,224
It was a partnership.

216
00:18:34,432 --> 00:18:35,515
In Gangcheng,

217
00:18:35,849 --> 00:18:37,974
few companies are able to buy out

218
00:18:38,557 --> 00:18:39,557
your mother's shares.

219
00:18:47,557 --> 00:18:49,390
I'm done being controlled by Mom.

220
00:18:52,807 --> 00:18:53,807
Wait a moment.

221
00:18:54,890 --> 00:18:56,140
As for Xiaofan's job...

222
00:19:01,932 --> 00:19:02,932
I think

223
00:19:03,015 --> 00:19:05,140
we should still respect his wishes.

224
00:19:05,765 --> 00:19:08,349
He... has a mind of his own.

225
00:19:11,557 --> 00:19:13,515
Is that section chief
easy to get along with?

226
00:19:14,474 --> 00:19:15,849
He needs to be kept in line, too.

227
00:19:16,307 --> 00:19:17,307
He's timid.

228
00:19:18,349 --> 00:19:20,509
Send the two cartons of
cigarettes in the trunk to him.

229
00:19:21,265 --> 00:19:22,908
Can't let the relationship
turn sour, either.

230
00:19:22,932 --> 00:19:24,765
This is our new deputy section chief,

231
00:19:24,932 --> 00:19:25,932
Lu Xiaofan.

232
00:19:26,140 --> 00:19:26,682
From now on,

233
00:19:26,765 --> 00:19:28,349
please support his work.

234
00:19:29,599 --> 00:19:30,599
If he settles in well,

235
00:19:31,099 --> 00:19:32,474
let him stay there for now.

236
00:19:34,182 --> 00:19:35,182
As for the rest...

237
00:19:37,182 --> 00:19:38,182
Two years.

238
00:19:38,849 --> 00:19:40,181
Two years is enough time

239
00:19:40,182 --> 00:19:41,765
to cash out my mother's shares.

240
00:19:42,265 --> 00:19:43,390
We'll deal with it then.

241
00:19:53,849 --> 00:19:54,849
Drink up!

242
00:19:54,974 --> 00:19:55,974
Drink up!

243
00:19:56,474 --> 00:19:57,474
Drink up!

244
00:19:57,807 --> 00:19:58,890
Drink up!

245
00:19:59,182 --> 00:19:59,474
Drink up!

246
00:19:59,475 --> 00:20:01,515
It's your birthday, yet
I'm the one stuck drinking.

247
00:20:03,974 --> 00:20:05,099
Hey, isn't that Lu Xiaofan?

248
00:20:14,974 --> 00:20:16,099
Ran off pretty fast.

249
00:20:23,182 --> 00:20:24,599
Thanks for having my back, bro.

250
00:20:25,640 --> 00:20:26,807
I'm very grateful to you.

251
00:20:30,182 --> 00:20:31,182
It was you who told him?

252
00:20:31,599 --> 00:20:33,181
I just thought you might want to

253
00:20:33,182 --> 00:20:34,599
experience having one on each arm.

254
00:20:35,224 --> 00:20:36,224
You did that on purpose.

255
00:21:58,893 --> 00:21:59,893
(Two years later, 1992)

256
00:22:06,057 --> 00:22:07,140
Hey, isn't that Xiaofan?

257
00:22:07,765 --> 00:22:09,390
Want to join us for abalone?

258
00:22:09,890 --> 00:22:10,890
Your bro's coming too.

259
00:22:19,307 --> 00:22:20,390
Ziyang.

260
00:22:20,682 --> 00:22:22,182
I have something to do,

261
00:22:22,682 --> 00:22:23,682
so I'll pass.

262
00:22:28,307 --> 00:22:29,307
All for nothing.

263
00:22:34,890 --> 00:22:35,931
My dear Master Bei,

264
00:22:35,932 --> 00:22:38,390
why are you tangled up with him again?

265
00:22:40,265 --> 00:22:41,265
I'm not.

266
00:22:41,515 --> 00:22:42,515
Come on,

267
00:22:42,807 --> 00:22:44,182
You went through so much trouble

268
00:22:44,307 --> 00:22:46,307
just to break free from your mother.

269
00:22:46,474 --> 00:22:48,015
And now all of this is for Lu Xiaofan?

270
00:22:48,640 --> 00:22:49,640
Enough.

271
00:22:49,932 --> 00:22:50,557
Stop running your mouth.

272
00:22:50,890 --> 00:22:52,250
What are you really trying to say?

273
00:22:52,724 --> 00:22:55,224
You backed him openly
and privately these two years.

274
00:22:55,724 --> 00:22:56,515
In your heart,

275
00:22:56,516 --> 00:22:58,349
he's no simple page boy anymore, right?

276
00:22:58,432 --> 00:23:01,015
If you worried Mom
would hurt him back then,

277
00:23:01,140 --> 00:23:02,890
you could've told him straight.

278
00:23:09,099 --> 00:23:10,265
I want to go buy a cake.

279
00:23:10,974 --> 00:23:12,099
Today is Xiaofan's birthday.

280
00:23:13,057 --> 00:23:14,556
So you do know how to sweet-talk him.

281
00:23:14,557 --> 00:23:16,116
A rabbit won't eat grass near its burrow,

282
00:23:16,140 --> 00:23:17,932
nor will a fine horse turn back to graze.

283
00:23:18,307 --> 00:23:20,765
I just can't figure out his appeal at all.

284
00:23:22,307 --> 00:23:23,547
Of course you don't understand.

285
00:23:26,182 --> 00:23:27,182
When I was little,

286
00:23:27,349 --> 00:23:29,182
we had a housekeeper called Aunt Zhang.

287
00:23:29,724 --> 00:23:31,140
I was especially attached to her.

288
00:23:31,432 --> 00:23:32,682
I would only eat food she made.

289
00:23:33,724 --> 00:23:34,515
One day,

290
00:23:34,682 --> 00:23:36,265
when she was bringing my meal upstairs,

291
00:23:36,515 --> 00:23:37,890
the spoon fell on the floor.

292
00:23:38,807 --> 00:23:39,807
She picked it up

293
00:23:40,557 --> 00:23:41,797
and handed it right back to me.

294
00:23:42,557 --> 00:23:43,557
I've often thought.

295
00:23:44,724 --> 00:23:46,807
If I were her own child,

296
00:23:47,349 --> 00:23:48,764
would she have taken the trouble

297
00:23:48,765 --> 00:23:50,682
to go downstairs and fetch me a new spoon?

298
00:23:53,432 --> 00:23:54,557
You're saying...

299
00:23:55,182 --> 00:23:56,849
Lu Xiaofan would get you the clean spoon.

300
00:23:59,557 --> 00:24:00,557
Now,

301
00:24:01,099 --> 00:24:02,931
no dropped spoons.

302
00:24:02,932 --> 00:24:03,724
All right, all right.

303
00:24:03,849 --> 00:24:04,974
There you go again.

304
00:24:07,599 --> 00:24:08,974
Don't tease him anymore.

305
00:24:09,474 --> 00:24:10,890
Lu Xiaofan takes things seriously.

306
00:24:24,765 --> 00:24:25,807
Come back.

307
00:24:47,057 --> 00:24:48,057
Bro.

308
00:24:48,765 --> 00:24:49,932
What are you doing back?

309
00:24:59,724 --> 00:25:00,724
I bought an extra one,

310
00:25:01,182 --> 00:25:02,182
so I brought it home.

311
00:25:08,390 --> 00:25:09,390
Bro.

312
00:25:10,724 --> 00:25:12,682
Can you wish me a happy birthday?

313
00:25:16,974 --> 00:25:17,974
Happy birthday.

314
00:25:45,265 --> 00:25:46,265
Wait.

315
00:26:02,140 --> 00:26:03,140
There.

316
00:26:08,307 --> 00:26:11,140
Happy birthday to you.

317
00:26:11,932 --> 00:26:14,682
Happy birthday to you.

318
00:26:15,807 --> 00:26:18,599
Happy birthday, dear Xiaofan.

319
00:26:22,182 --> 00:26:24,932
Happy birthday to you.

320
00:26:33,015 --> 00:26:34,015
All right.

321
00:26:35,182 --> 00:26:36,182
Blow out the candles.

322
00:26:56,140 --> 00:26:57,140
Happy birthday.

323
00:26:58,890 --> 00:26:59,890
Thank you, bro.

324
00:27:07,432 --> 00:27:09,182
This cake is just as good as before.

325
00:27:13,932 --> 00:27:15,349
There's nothing good after this.

326
00:27:15,474 --> 00:27:16,474
Bro,

327
00:27:16,849 --> 00:27:18,329
you can watch the international news.

328
00:27:20,390 --> 00:27:21,390
It's fine.

329
00:27:22,390 --> 00:27:24,182
I can watch these anytime.

330
00:27:24,474 --> 00:27:25,474
It's okay.

331
00:27:26,807 --> 00:27:28,474
No need, I'll leave right away.

332
00:27:28,682 --> 00:27:30,057
I said, I want to watch it.

333
00:27:33,640 --> 00:27:34,640
Come back.

334
00:29:56,849 --> 00:29:57,849
Tomorrow...

335
00:29:59,015 --> 00:30:00,015
make me congee.

336
00:30:23,586 --> 00:30:26,033
[Bei Lüqing: Call when you're free]

337
00:30:46,224 --> 00:30:47,533
What took you so long to call back?

338
00:30:47,557 --> 00:30:48,765
I was at the office.

339
00:30:49,224 --> 00:30:50,224
Couldn't really talk.

340
00:30:50,724 --> 00:30:51,724
I'm at the supermarket.

341
00:30:51,807 --> 00:30:52,557
What do you need?
I'll pick it up for you.

342
00:30:54,015 --> 00:30:55,974
We already bought
scallions, ginger and garlic.

343
00:30:56,557 --> 00:30:57,557
So...

344
00:30:58,015 --> 00:30:59,015
get half a chicken,

345
00:30:59,140 --> 00:30:59,974
a fish.

346
00:31:00,015 --> 00:31:01,265
Just pick whatever looks fresh.

347
00:31:01,557 --> 00:31:02,682
And some leafy greens.

348
00:31:02,724 --> 00:31:03,724
Get what you want to eat.

349
00:31:03,874 --> 00:31:04,392
Oh, right,

350
00:31:04,557 --> 00:31:05,557
and some eggs.

351
00:31:05,890 --> 00:31:06,890
Okay, got it.

352
00:31:07,724 --> 00:31:08,890
Just get what you like.

353
00:31:09,515 --> 00:31:10,724
Go wait at my place.

354
00:31:10,849 --> 00:31:12,015
I'll be back soon.
